            PubMed
        </a></p><p class="reference" id="j_cdbme-2016-0037_ref_003_w2aab3b7d254b1b6b1ab2b1b3Aa"><span class="reference-label d-inlineblock me-4">[3] </span><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Rottmann M, Keller MW, Oesterlein T, Seemann G, Dössel O. Comparison of different methods and catheter designs to estimate the rotor tip position – a simulation study. CinC. 2014:133–6.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Rottmann%20M%2C%20Keller%20MW%2C%20Oesterlein%20T%2C%20Seemann%20G%2C%20D%C3%B6ssel%20O.%20Comparison%20of%20different%20methods%20and%20catheter%20designs%20to%20estimate%20the%20rotor%20tip%20position%20%E2%80%93%20a%20simulation%20study.%20CinC.%202014%3A133%E2%80%936." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_cdbme-2016-0037_ref_004_w2aab3b7d254b1b6b1ab2b1b4Aa"><span class="reference-label d-inlineblock me-4">[4] </span><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Rottmann M, Unger L, Kaltenbacher W, Seemann G, Loewe A, Krueger MW, et al. Methods for analyzing signal characteristics of stable and unstable rotors in a realistic heart model. CinC. 2015:485–8.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/CIC.2015.7410953" class="link link-external doi" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">10.1109/CIC.2015.7410953</a><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Rottmann%20M%2C%20Unger%20L%2C%20Kaltenbacher%20W%2C%20Seemann%20G%2C%20Loewe%20A%2C%20Krueger%20MW%2C%20et%20al.%20Methods%20for%20analyzing%20signal%20characteristics%20of%20stable%20and%20unstable%20rotors%20in%20a%20realistic%20heart%20model.%20CinC.%202015%3A485%E2%80%938." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_cdbme-2016-0037_ref_005_w2aab3b7d254b1b6b1ab2b1b5Aa"><span cla